### How to Reproduce?

Using image but was able to reproduce with local executable as well


For reproducing use the file name `test-realm.json`, `test-realm-realm.json` and `realm-test.json`. First will fail to start.

When running the following command don't forget change the entry point `path-to-ream-file`.
Run `docker run -p 8080:8080 -v <path-to-ream-file>:/opt/keycloak/data/import -e KC_BOOTSTRAP_ADMIN_USERNAME=admin -e KC_BOOTSTRAP_ADMIN_PASSWORD=admin quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:26.0.7 start-dev --hostname-strict=false --import-realm`

